title: 820-01521 won't turn on
message:
820-01521 (Macbook air 2018) no sign of liquid spill. Customer said that it just shut off suddenly and wouldn't turn on again and that it was more and more warm with time before it died. 
Without battery connected it measures 5V and takes 0,40A for 2-3 seconds, then 0A and again 0,40A.
With battery connected it goes to 20V but takes 0A.

title: 820-01521 won't turn on
message:
Check which voltages appear on the board, with charger only.
Be sure no short on any big coil.
